metadata.name: Baby Villains #1
metadata.description: Baby Villains is a collection of 6666 NFTs living in the Ethereum blockchainThe Baby Villains are stored as ERC-721 tokens and hosted on IPFSWith upwards of 150+ hand drawn traits, each NFT grants you membership to a select play-to-earn game, where you’ll be able ot earn rewards, while simultaneously having fun with other community membersBenefits include holders only events, masterminds, access to (TBA)—a bustling digital city that will be built and developed on the metaverse, and much moreOur team is committed to building the world's premier web 3.0 project together with our amazing community, impelled by our fascination for digital collectibles, gaming, and the metaverse.
